Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,朋君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为父亲再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来了个奇怪的姐姐
